[01:37.33] This is the story of a starry night,
[01:49.48] The faded glory of a new delight
[02:00.65] One breathless meeting,
[02:06.64] Two lips repeating
[02:12.80] Three precious words that were sweet but fleeting...
[02:38.80] 
[02:25.69] When stars are bright my heart keeps wondering why
[02:38.92] Our first "goodnight" became our last goodbye
[02:50.38] I pray that someday
[02:56.45] Love will in some way
[03:02.32] Bring back the story of a starry night...